9.1  Onboarding Completion Definition

An onboarding session is considered "complete" when the tenant has achieved at least one of the following milestones. These are tracked in tenant.metadata.onboarding_complete_at.

OIDC: First app created AND at least one user other than the owner exists in the workspace

SAML: First SAML SP registered AND IdP metadata successfully downloaded or copied

SCIM: SCIM enabled, token copied, AND at least one user provisioned via SCIM

Federation: First IdP registered AND test authentication completed successfully



